### 🟡 MEDIUM

#### 6. No Global Error Handler — Potential Stack Trace Leakage (OWASP A05:2021)

If any route throws, Express's default error handler will send the full stack trace to the client in development mode, and may still leak details in production.

**Fix:** Add an error-handling middleware as the very last `app.use`:

```js
