There is zero request logging. Security events (failed auth, unexpected inputs) are invisible.

**Fix:** Add [`morgan`](https://github.com/expressjs/morgan) for access logs and emit structured security events:

```js
const morgan = require('morgan');
app.use(morgan('combined')); // Apache-style access log; pipe to a SIEM in production
